Key bindings
  m          Toggle shaders
  o          Change objects
  t			 Change textures
  s          Toggle light movement
  <>+-       Move light
  arrows     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit


